* Liquid Clustering\nas Alternative
** Advantages over Partitioning
***_ Change strategy without rewriting data
***_ Supports up to 4 clustering keys
***_ Works for tables < 1 TB too
** When to Prefer Liquid Clustering
***_ Query patterns uncertain / evolving
***_ Table < 1 TB not needing partitioning
***_ Multiple filter columns
** Migration Path
***_ Add CLUSTER BY to unpartitioned table
***_ Run OPTIMIZE to apply
***_ Use CLUSTER BY AUTO for self-tuning
@endmindmap
